## GSD Workflow Integration

### Per-Phase Workflow

For every phase, follow the GSD workflow in order:

```
/gsd-discuss-phase <n>  →  /gsd-plan-phase <n>  →  /gsd-execute-phase <n>  →  /gsd-transition
```

Do not skip the discuss-phase — it captures decisions in `.planning/phases/<phase>/NN-CONTEXT.md` that inform planning and execution.

### Discuss-Phase Outputs

After `/gsd-discuss-phase`, these files must exist:

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `.planning/phases/NN-Name/NN-CONTEXT.md` | Captured decisions, boundaries, spec references |
| `.planning/phases/NN-Name/NN-DISCUSSION-LOG.md` | Audit trail of Q&A choices |

### Plan-Phase Outputs

After `/gsd-plan-phase`, these files must exist:

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `.planning/phases/NN-Name/NN-PLAN.md` | Wave-based task breakdown |
| `.planning/phases/NN-Name/NN-PLAN-CHECK.md` | Blockers and warnings from plan-checker |

If `NN-PLAN-CHECK.md` has BLOCKER items, resolve them before executing.

### Transition Outputs

After `/gsd-transition`, these files must be updated:

| File | Action |
|------|--------|
| `.planning/STATE.md` | Refresh project reference, update phase progress |
| `.planning/PROJECT.md` | Move REQs: Active → Validated or Out of Scope |
| `docs/roadmap/README.md` | Mark phase status: Pending → Done |
| `docs/roadmap/module_index.md` | Update module status: TBD → READY |

