## Per-Module Validation Checklist

### Types
- [ ] GPSI regex: `^5[0-9]{8,14}$`
- [ ] SUPI regex: `^imu-[0-9]{15}$`
- [ ] Snssai SST: 0-255
- [ ] Snssai SD: 6 hex chars

### API Handlers
- [ ] Request validation before processing
- [ ] Error response: ProblemDetails (RFC 7807)
- [ ] HTTP status: 201, 200, 400, 403, 404, 409, 410, 502, 503, 504
- [ ] Location header on 201
- [ ] X-Request-ID correlation

### Storage
- [ ] GPSI hashed in audit log
- [ ] Session state encrypted
- [ ] Monthly partitions
- [ ] Redis TTL

### Tests
- [ ] Unit test for each public function
- [ ] Validate error cases
- [ ] Mock external dependencies

> **Skill:** See `.cursor/skills/golang-testing/SKILL.md` for table-driven test patterns, interface-based mocking, golden files, benchmarks, and TDD workflow.

